Ruby Application Template
-------------------------

You need korundum4 from KDE 4 kdebindings module or from your distribution to run this template.

Build it
--------
cd /your_app
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make 
make install

Run it
------
krubyapplication your_app your-app/main.rb


Tutorials
---------
You'll find a KDE Ruby tutorial in kdebindings svn source code
http://websvn.kde.org/trunk/KDE/kdebindings/ruby/korundum/tutorials/
or via anonymous svn
svn co svn://anonsvn.kde.org/home/kde/trunk/KDE/kdebindings/ruby/korundum/tutorials/

Qt4 Ruby Tutorial
http://www.darshancomputing.com/qt4-qtruby-tutorial/
